{"tid":1512686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米微博踩界玩「五大平台 缺一不可」 官媒狠批冇腦：無藥可救","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T03:51:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"782ca04f10c9d2fbff6c8a6755ade48b4f7935b1","tid":1512686,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/4324234234234.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F4324234234234.jpg&h=d77eab82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190827/large/1566895723_a4fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566895723_a4fb.jpg&h=7f3d70fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【新增影片】屢傳出公關災難的小米（1810）繼昨日高層減持風波後，今日再惹爭端！今日早上，小米旗下快將推出的紅米電視，其官方微博發圖，並展示「五大平台 缺一不可」 用來宣傳5大電視App。<br />\n<br />\n圖片上載後，不久被官媒環球網發現，並留言「缺腦如此、無藥可救」，不久被小米發現，立即將圖片刪除，並改成「海量內容」，環球網亦回覆指「知錯就改，加強學習」，紅米電視微博現時雖沒有「被關閉」，但已看不到該圖片的留言。<br />\n<br />\n事件即引來大量網民轉發，有網友將圖片與「港獨」掛鈎，指即使在美國提及911也會被調查。有網民為小米護航，指「五星紅旗缺一不可」、「現代紅衛兵」；有人認為環球網過份敏感，表示「好大的官威啊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190827/59978894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F59978894&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQyF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=eaae77ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F59978894&h=d8e098e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190827/59978894</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a6d0e4f3bd5511ccd79a97bb6b9933f97c8725","tid":1512686,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r